headline: Alliant Energy (LNT) Beats Q2 Earnings Estimates
summary: Alliant Energy (LNT) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of +9.68% and -2.67%, respectively, for the quarter ended June 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
